## Changelog
### Features
* 621379b0c85082840529a2460954d5a13353569a feat: Add --git-lfs option to init command
* 82e5c670c293dc765327155365c9b8152bed28cb feat: Add builtin mode for gopass
* 21ef18698e40e4aa29c8433943fb041ced89b8f3 feat: Improve placeholders in password prompts
* 48e23ff7eb976ccead098a7128cf26ec9d960f0f feat: Show all contributors in README.md
### Fixes
* 940cc30642a0ec02d45ec59fa37358f899e4fd2b fix: Fix doctor command when --config is specified
* fc8c20f921eecbe20b01c98e54eb4d3b15ec42de fix: Correct nested groups for keepassxc builtin mode
* dda281698671c4a4404d04b7f11461c3b4ca908a fix: Suppress gitleaks logspam
### Documentation updates
* 6c4431e430d4ad45b10bd44e711bd5d5c64ed5a5 docs: Tidy up formatting as suggested by markdownlint
